# Banner demo: two posts along the tile edge (OBJ +Z) with a sign between them.
# Rear post is *PostBack* (back sprite); front post + sign are the front sprite.
# OBJ space: +X forward (depth), +Y up, +Z along the edge. Normals from loader.
mtllib materials.mtl

# Rear post (z ~= -1.5)
v -0.06 0.0 -1.56
v  0.06 0.0 -1.56
v  0.06 1.6 -1.56
v -0.06 1.6 -1.56
v -0.06 0.0 -1.44
v  0.06 0.0 -1.44
v  0.06 1.6 -1.44
v -0.06 1.6 -1.44

# Front post (z ~= +1.5)
v -0.06 0.0 1.44
v  0.06 0.0 1.44
v  0.06 1.6 1.44
v -0.06 1.6 1.44
v -0.06 0.0 1.56
v  0.06 0.0 1.56
v  0.06 1.6 1.56
v -0.06 1.6 1.56

# Sign panel (spans between the posts, near the top)
v -0.03 1.00 -1.40
v  0.03 1.00 -1.40
v  0.03 1.55 -1.40
v -0.03 1.55 -1.40
v -0.03 1.00 1.40
v  0.03 1.00 1.40
v  0.03 1.55 1.40
v -0.03 1.55 1.40

usemtl PostBack
